name: The Road #2
description:
The Road #2 is an ongoing mini series based on the escapades of the past and future. 

Every image shot while driving.

Shot on - Nikon AF with Ektar 100 film on Navajo Nation - Route 66 - Holbrook, Arizona, in October 2019. Un-edited and raw.

The Mother Road (Route 66) is the best and worst America has to offer. 

As historian Michael Wallis said, "Route 66 has always been a mirror held to reflect what goes on in the nation:''

Poppi
